latestIgtvVideos.title: I tried the NEW Dyson Corrale hair straightener!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Home styling is really not my thing, but I guess we need to adapt to the changing times where getting your hair done at a salon is just not as convenient as it used to be! 
I’m all for easy use and convenience when it comes to grooming tools, which is why I truly appreciate it when products make your life a tad bit easier.  Here’s everything you need to know about the new @dyson_india Corrale CORD FREE hair straightener and all the reasons I love it!

💜 The only straightener with flexing plates that shape to gather hair
💜 HALF the damage against your usual hair straighteners due to the intelligent heat control system 
💜 Cord free styling makes is so easy to carry around and use anywhere 
💜 Ready to travel - universal voltage & flight ready feature
.
